    "tone": "Highly technical, data-driven, highly opinionated, slightly cynical, and internet-native.",
    "target_audience": "AI infrastructure engineers, ML researchers, semiconductor analysts, and tech investors.",
    "translation_voice": "Authoritative and precise on ML and hardware engineering concepts, but unapologetically sharp and colloquial when delivering critiques (matching the original's 'tech-bro' / internet slang flavor)."
  },
